trans-unit.source: The WebBrowser control provides the following capabilities: **Navigation**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.
trans-unit.target: WebBrowser 컨트롤은 다음과 같은 기능을 제공: **탐색**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Refresh%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToString%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.NavigateToStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Navigation Lifetime**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.
trans-unit.target: **탐색 수명**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigated> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigating>

trans-unit.source: **Navigation Journaling**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **탐색 저널링**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>

trans-unit.source: **WPF/HTML Interoperability**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>.
trans-unit.target: **WPF/HTML 상호 운용성**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A>및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A>, 및 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Document%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.ObjectForScripting%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%2A>

trans-unit.source: WebBrowser is bound by the security constraints of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] application that is hosting the WebBrowser: - When WebBrowser is hosted by a full-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] application (a stand-alone application, for example), WebBrowser can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documents from any location.
trans-unit.target: WebBrowser의 보안 제약 조건에 의해 바인딩된는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] WebBrowser를 호스팅하는 응용 프로그램:-WebBrowser 완전 신뢰에서 호스팅되는 경우 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 응용 프로그램 (독립 실행형 응용 프로그램, 예:), WebBrowser를 호스트할 수 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] 어느 위치에서 문서입니다.

trans-unit.source: - When WebBrowser is hosted by a partial-trust [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] application (an [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], for example), WebBrowser can only host documents that are **Site Of Origin** application data files.
trans-unit.target: -WebBrowser 부분 신뢰에서 호스트 된 경우 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 응용 프로그램 (한 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]예를 들어,), WebBrowser 문서를 호스팅할 수 있습니다 **원본 사이트** 응용 프로그램 데이터 파일.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [WPF Application Resource, Content, and Data Files](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 참조 [WPF 응용 프로그램 리소스, 내용 및 데이터 파일](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: WPF enables security features by applying feature controls to the WebBrowser ActiveX control.

trans-unit.source: The feature controls that are applied differ for XBAPs and stand-alone applications.
trans-unit.target: 적용 되는 기능 컨트롤 Xbap 및 독립 실행형 응용 프로그램 마다 다릅니다.

trans-unit.source: Some applications should apply additional feature controls to prevent malicious content from running.
trans-unit.target: 일부 응용 프로그램의 실행 악의적인 내용을 방지 하기 위해 추가 기능 컨트롤에 적용 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the "WebBrowser Control and Feature Controls" section in [Security (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [WebBrowser Control Overviews and Tutorials](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=179388).
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은의 "WebBrowser 컨트롤 및 기능 컨트롤" 섹션을 참조 하십시오. [보안 (WPF)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) 및 [WebBrowser 컨트롤 개요 및 자습서](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=179388)합니다.
